## API Notes (from test findings):
- Grammar evaluate with 50 rules triggers all of them (variable scoping issue)
- Rule named "medium" shadows Python eval context
- Stream uses `observations` field, not `n`
- No `disconnect` method on Fleet
- `submit_batch([])` returns `[]` (good)

